{"id":1274714107,"question_id":3430,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"3 weeks, 2 days","timestamp":1717296695,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"35 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1274714107/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Count Days Without Meetings","memory":"100.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int countDays(int days, int[][] meetings) {\n        Arrays.sort(meetings, (a,b)->a[0]-b[0]);\n        \n        int count = 0;\n        int low = -1, high = -1;\n        for(int i=0;i<meetings.length;i++){\n            if(low == -1){\n                low = meetings[i][0];\n                high = meetings[i][1];\n                count+=(low-1);\n            }else if(meetings[i][0]<=high){\n                high = Math.max(high, meetings[i][1]);\n            }else{\n                low = meetings[i][0];\n                count+=(low-high-1);\n                high = meetings[i][1];\n            }\n        }\n        \n        count+=(days-high);\n        \n        return count;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"count-days-without-meetings","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
